lity, peer-reviewed scholarship accessible once again using print-on-demand technology. This title was originally published in 1974.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mrz 2024) 0aAcademic writing. 0aHistoriography. 0aHistoryxResearch. 4ahistorical research. 4ahistoriography. 4ahistory. 4aresearch. 4awriting. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520311923?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520311923423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520311923/original  aEBA_EMB  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles